
these are the people who are allowed to run things as root

do you see how I dont have to put anything weird like comment tags in this file?

incredible, right?

Like, as long as you never have two question marks or two exclamation marks in a row,
you will never interfere with the function of the program.

You will make it slightly slower, though, so maybe don't write a book in here.

To add yourself, just enter your unix username surrounded in two question marks anywhere in this file.

These people are allowed to login without entering their password:

??gek??
??pi??

These people have to type it:

!!richardstallman!!
